{"tid":749124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"倉鼠乸究竟諗咩？？","createTime":"2018-07-19T18:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T20:33:03.000Z","uid":179169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1466c6f078004ec2225c78cd249a4279770cab35","tid":749124,"uid":179169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"一公一乸最近將佢地合寵 <br />\n察覺公鼠病左所以分籠<br />\n病左一直冇咩點理個乸<br />\n隻乸每次見到我就沖過黎咬籠<br />\n因為要每日幫公鼠換野<br />\n開頭我換緊唔理佢咬籠咬咬下會停<br />\n今日我換幾耐佢咬幾耐<br />\n諗住換兜野食俾佢分散注意力<br />\n但仲繼續咬 要喂到埋口先識停<br />\n<br />\n我拎佢上手就係咁咬我 都唔知理唔理佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係想搵隻公鼠定想點？？"},{"pid":"bd25382858183259f4fe13e57be932b32097be31","tid":749124,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"佢呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c273e053549793da670b4f600654e348702123b","tid":749124,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:24:58.000Z","msg":"想得到你注意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b69297ee28e2ccd4001a9c3642a591e00066c7f","tid":749124,"uid":179169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd25382858183259f4fe13e57be932b32097be31","tid":749124,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"佢呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"倉鼠都識呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我再注意佢睇怕咬到我流血為止"},{"pid":"8f48648bcd479fddf8d072044ff473c31c2a9b55","tid":749124,"uid":38244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"你抱孫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547e46d8072138e937e12fb056831bd7724a394f","tid":749124,"uid":179169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f48648bcd479fddf8d0